@startuml
title UC-18 Audit Log / System Logs (Sequence)
participant Actor
participant WebApp
participant AuditService
participant DB
participant AlertService
participant Admin

Actor -> WebApp: perform action (create/update/delete)
WebApp -> AuditService: record(actorId, action, resource, before, after)
AuditService -> DB: INSERT audit_log
DB --> AuditService: saved
alt alert rule matched
AuditService -> AlertService: sendAlert(details)
AlertService -> Admin: email/Slack alert
end
AuditService --> WebApp: ack
WebApp --> Actor: continue
@enduml
